name: Teal Blue Jacks Bookends- Mid Century Modern Style Jax Book Ends or Paperweights
description:
Looking to add a memory of your childhood to your home or office? These oversized large cast iron jacks will add not only style but a conversation piece to any space. They are made of heavy cast iron and can be used as sculptural accents, paperweights or doorstops. They make excellent bookends. 

These jacks are hand finished in a fun and retro teal blue. This order includes a set of 2 jacks.

These would make a nice gift for the book lover in your life or the vintage decor enthusiast.
